OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMostly cloudy with some bright
OL,6,Fspells. It will be mainly dry in the
OL,7,Fmorning, a few afternoon showers
OL,8,Fdeveloping and these turning sharp in
OL,9,Fplaces.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA largely dry but rather
OL,12,Fcloudy evening. Overnight, conditions
OL,13,Fwill stay dry for most areas, though a
OL,14,Ffew isolated showers may develop later
OL,15,Fin the west.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FA dry and bright start to the
OL,18,Fday with patchy cloud. A few showers
OL,19,Fmay develop from late morning, these
OL,20,Fmostly light and clearing away through
OL,21,Fthe afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
